<!-- ============================= -->
<!-- = myPostit By Laurent Vanni = -->
<!-- ============================= -->

myPostit is a Proof Of Concept for the cChord engine: 
see https://github.com/MrGando/cChord

<!-- ============ -->
<!-- = Building = -->
<!-- ============ -->
First build the cChord Engine : see lib/cChord/src/README
Then build mypostit:
$make

<!-- ========= -->
<!-- = Usage = -->
<!-- ========= -->
Usage: myPostit [-v|--version] [-p|--port <PORTNUMBER>] [-h|--help]
example: to start myPostit on port 8000

$./myPostit -p 8000

Then access to the UI on: http://127.0.0.1:8000

(the port option is not mandatory, the default port is 8000)

To join an existing cChord ring you can edit the MyPostit.cpp file and add new existing seeds (see the backbone array)


